WEBVTT

00:01.233 --> 00:02.366
Come on, let's see this at 7:30.

00:02.433 --> 00:03.800
‐ Then I want to see this‐‐
‐ 'So, ladies..'

00:05.666 --> 00:07.166
Y'all..

00:09.600 --> 00:11.300
Y'all picked the flick? Huh?

00:11.366 --> 00:13.833
I'm with, I'm with anything as
long as it is not one of those

00:13.900 --> 00:16.332
all men are dogs, burn his cot.

00:16.400 --> 00:20.166
Denzel come
and save my life, chick flicks.

00:20.233 --> 00:21.466
Like you didn't cry buckets

00:21.533 --> 00:23.200
when Big Mama died
in "Soul Food."

00:25.300 --> 00:27.600
Big Mama
meant everything to them girls.

