♪ Hey ♪

00:33.933 --> 00:35.566
♪ Single ♪

00:35.633 --> 00:38.166
♪ Ooh and in a nineties
kinda world ♪

00:38.233 --> 00:40.600
♪ I'm glad I got my girls ♪

00:40.666 --> 00:41.900
♪ Keep your head up ♪
♪ What? ♪

00:41.966 --> 00:43.266
♪ Keep your head up ♪
♪ That's right ♪

00:43.333 --> 00:45.166
♪ Whenever this life get tough
you gotta fight ♪

00:45.233 --> 00:47.400
♪ With my homegirls standing
to my left and my right ♪

00:47.466 --> 00:49.333
♪ True blue
it's tight like glue ♪

00:49.400 --> 00:51.066
♪ We are living ♪
